{"tid":1560142,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］其實Sunny憎撚到佢個警犬老豆仆街","createTime":"2019-09-11T05:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T18:36:30.000Z","uid":48124,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae0402894d7a47705d662242c44090d3f56d0bb","tid":1560142,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"Copy from 另一個post既巴打<br />\n<br />\n其實Sunny憎撚到佢個警犬老豆仆街<br />\n父母一早離左婚，跟阿媽生活。<br />\n自己聽下鐵樹蘭首&lt;&lt;荷理活道&gt;&gt;，即係已婚警察宿舍<br />\n利申:唔係洗白，鐘意聽鐵記多過supper<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rEBUn8pFM0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrEBUn8pFM0g&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=f44ecb7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rEBUn8pFM0g</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">從小已沒有爸爸去給我一個可靠的肩膀</span><br />\n無奈她說要向著所想快樂奔往<br />\n你說怎麼 我可以怎麼<br />\n由你離開這一家思憶每日把我折磨<br />\n從前回家的踢嗒踢嗒 孩子再沒有聽過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">並未忘記爸爸那天狠狠地向媽媽批鬥</span><br />\n並未忘記細小身軀依偎一角驚慌戰抖<br />\n-------<br />\n當然, Supper 2013 年演唱會opening時播曬反國教、HKTV集會、噓689....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家笠曬水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個唔屌唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75548db26b92f50a641f6e282d8b978dab9f43e2","tid":1560142,"uid":255233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:53:56.000Z","msg":"915銅鑼灣 915銅鑼灣 915銅鑼灣<br />\n少少行動分析 入嚟幫手一齊諗一齊討論<br />\n求幫推 求share<br />\n<br />\n［915集思廣益］去民陣遊行嘅入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559801</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4e504e9bacb661e92f9c4dde88b626fe731db0","tid":1560142,"uid":73404,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 打手<img sr